title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18 §§ 358-2.25 - Witness
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18 §§ 358-2.25 - Witness

State Regulations

Witness means a person, other than the applicant, recipient, or the representative thereof, who presents testimony and/or
documentary evidence at a fair hearing. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18
